msgid "# LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2-0.5B-OV"
msgstr "# LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2-0.5B-OV"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"`llava-hf/llava-onevision-qwen2-0.5b-ov-hf` is a compact multimodal model "
"built on top of Qwen2. It supports text-only generation together with image "
"understanding, multi-image reasoning, and visual dialogue."
msgstr ""
"`llava-hf/llava-onevision-qwen2-0.5b-ov-hf` 是一个基于 Qwen2 "
"构建的紧凑型多模态模型。它支持纯文本生成、图像理解、多图像推理以及视觉对话。"

msgid ""
"This document shows the main verification steps for the model on vLLM "
"Ascend, including environment preparation, single-NPU deployment, functional"
" verification, and the existing accuracy baseline used by the repository."
msgstr "本文档展示了该模型在 vLLM Ascend 上的主要验证步骤，包括环境准备、单 NPU 部署、功能验证以及仓库使用的现有精度基线。"

msgid "## Supported Features"
msgstr "## 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型的支持特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `llava-hf/llava-onevision-qwen2-0.5b-ov-hf`: [Download model "
"weight](https://huggingface.co/llava-hf/llava-onevision-qwen2-0.5b-ov-hf)"
msgstr ""
"- `llava-hf/llava-onevision-qwen2-0.5b-ov-"
"hf`：[下载模型权重](https://huggingface.co/llava-hf/llava-onevision-qwen2-0.5b-ov-"
"hf)"

msgid ""
"The verified single-card deployment uses one Atlas A2 NPU. It is recommended"
" to cache model weights under `/root/.cache` in advance to reduce startup "
"time."
msgstr "已验证的单卡部署使用一块 Atlas A2 NPU。建议提前将模型权重缓存到 `/root/.cache` 目录下，以减少启动时间。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid ""
"You can use the official docker image to run `LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2-0.5B-OV`"
" directly."
msgstr "您可以直接使用官方 Docker 镜像运行 `LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2-0.5B-OV`。"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动 Docker 镜像，请参考[使用 Docker](../../installation.md#set-up-"
"using-docker)。"

